flowchart TD
  A[Opportunity: city + service] --> B{Subdomain or path?}
  B -- Subdomain --> C[city.customer-domain.de]
  B -- Path --> D[customer-domain.de/orte/city]
  C --> E[Template + components]
  D --> E
  E --> F[Content + local proof]
